  "designNotes": "The Creative template makes no apologies for being loud — near-black backgrounds create a gallery void that lets visual work breathe, while the hot pink / electric blue / neon yellow triad delivers the visual punch that stops a scroll in the GCC social media landscape. The animated gradient hero name is the signature: an infinitely cycling Syne 800-weight headline that communicates personality before a single word is processed. Print output functions as a media kit with portfolio thumbnails, static brand logos, and QR codes for video content."
